channel.title: Getting Server Online
channel.description: Okay.. So i have my server completed with a webclient on my website with auto cache downloader working and everything.. i can log in on it and play around. But it shows error connecting for others. I was told if you somehow put the client on dropbox others will be able to play "and see you" because everyone would be playing on the same client ip. So my question is.. is this true? and if so how can i put the client in the dropbox? .zip file on dropbox public? Any help appreciated thank you.
